{
  "stem": "22883.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I remember I took a bicycle because we were living a little bit outside of the-- well, not in the center of the city, so outside of the city.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And it was quite-- maybe two, three kilometers I had to go to school, and passing in the center of the city.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I took the bicycle, and I was driving, or riding, the bicycle to-- to-- to my high school.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And I had on my-- on me a uniform of that paramilitary organization, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "It's a-- it's a preparation for military service.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Because there was a rule that after graduating the high school, we have to go straight to-- to the military service.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And because we were entitled to go to military officer schools, therefore the-- the authorities wanted to spare all this drill in military.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "So we were having such drill in this paramilitary school-- paramilitary organization, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So when we-- we graduate and go to the-- to the military for the service, then we would go straight to the officer schools and not bother with-- with the soldiers' drill.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I had this uniform on, and I was riding this bicycle.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I came to the crossing of two larger street, and there a policeman was standing there, and he stopped me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he stopped me, and he came-- I-- I came to him and asked him why he is stopping me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he starts to-- to talk to me very gently and, you know, beating around the bushes.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So he said, I would not advise to you to go to the city because there are some groups, and they are doing nasty things.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So better go turn around and go to home.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
